<config xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:magento:module:Magento_Config:etc/system_file.xsd">
    <system>
        <tab id="auderecommerce_tab" translate="label" sortOrder="1000">
            <label>Audere Commerce</label>
        </tab>
        <section id="auderecommerce_accountsintegration" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
            <label>Accounts Integration</label>
            <tab>auderecommerce_tab</tab>
            <resource>AudereCommerce_AccountsIntegration::config</resource>
            <group id="product" type="select" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
                <label>Products</label>
                <field id="create" type="select" sortOrder="2" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
                    <label>Create new products</label>
                    <comment>Creates stock records as simple products with the default attribute set, status disabled, and visibility not visible individually. If enabled, mapped product attributes, base product prices, and product stock levels are also set on newly created products.</comment>
                    <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                </field>
                <field id="price" type="select" sortOrder="4" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
                    <label>Import product price</label>
                    <comment>Sets the value of the stock record sell price as the Magento product price.</comment>
                    <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                </field>
                <field id="price_bands" type="select" sortOrder="6" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
                    <label>Import price bands</label>
                    <comment>Stock record price bands are imported as customer group prices.</comment>
                    <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                </field>
                <field id="update_attributes" type="select" sortOrder="8" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
                    <label>Import product attributes</label>
                    <comment>If enabled, sets the value of the stock record field (left-hand side) against the mapped product attribute (right-hand side). Select/multiselect Magento product attribute values are automatically created. If using stock factoring, these values are set first before stock factors are applied.</comment>
                    <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                </field>
                <field id="update_attribute_cost_price" type="select" sortOrder="10" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
                    <label>Cost Price</label>
                    <source_model>AudereCommerce\AccountsIntegration\Model\Config\Source\Attributes</source_model>
                    <depends>
                        <field id="*/*/update_attributes">1</field>
                    </depends>
                </field>
                <field id="update_attribute_unit_description" type="select" sortOrder="15" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
